Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.13,Default,196,0,0,0,,不痛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.17,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:02.47,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,未來　我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:04.72,Default,390,0,0,0,,鏘！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.10,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:13.21,Default,390,0,0,0,,正合適　廣也一定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.57,Default,666,0,0,0,,喂！不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:20.78,Default,9a,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.03,Default,15,0,0,0,,你們幾個... 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:27.60,Default,9a,0,0,0,,來看看你們什麼情況　是爸爸吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:28.88,Default,56,0,0,0,,爸爸吩咐的?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:32.22,Default,56,0,0,0,,我們幾個...並沒有被拋棄嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.57,Default,9a,0,0,0,,當然沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:38.69,Default,9a,0,0,0,,不如說爸爸們一直都很擔心你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:41.21,Default,390,0,0,0,,太...太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:44.65,Default,666,0,0,0,,真是的　這種事要早點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.43,Default-Top,666,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.97,Default,9b,0,0,0,,話說回來　這可...
