Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.25,sign_white,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&HC6EDF5&\fscx1400\fscy400\blur4\alpha30\pos(255,83)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.53,Default,9a,0,0,0,,看樣子是有印象啊
